Title: Xamarin Developer Summit - Day 2
Description:
Join us for Day 2 of the Xamarin Developer Summit live from Houston, Texas! We will be live streaming throughout the entire day. See a full schedule at: https://xamarindevelopersummit.com/schedule

Schedule ( all in Central Time Zone (Houston, Texas)):

8:15AM: Xamarin in the Wild (Community Lightning Talks)
9:00AM: Keynote -  Mobile DevOps with Xamarin, App Center, and Azure DevOps - Donovan Brown
10:05AM: Building Xamarin.Android from Source – Jonathan Peppers
11:05AM: Create Mixed Reality Experiences with Azure Spatial Anchors and Xamarin – Sweekriti Satpathy
1:05PM: Let’s Make Crazy Beautiful UI with Xamarin.Forms – David Ortinau
2:05PM: Xamarin + GraphQL – Brandon Minnick
3:05PM: App Center and the future of Azure Mobile Apps – Patrick Nikoletich
4:05PM: Using Xamarin.Forms Shell – Shane Neuville
